    # Zt "Where is she?"
    Zt "¿Dónde está ella?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:28
translate spanish day1_end_c1a4e7dd:

    # Zt "I didn't hear anything during the night. She must've gotten out quietly."
    Zt "No oí nada durante la noche. Ella debió de salir en silencio."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:31
translate spanish day1_end_97a4fa3b:

    # Zt "But where could she be now?"
    Zt "Pero, ¿dónde podría estar ahora?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:32
translate spanish day1_end_eea23102:

    # Zt "It seems she at least ate something..."
    Zt "Parece que al menos comió algo..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:41
translate spanish d2a_home_efb871cc:

    # Zt "She could be anywhere."
    Zt "Ella podría estar en cualquier parte."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:42
translate spanish d2a_home_16be445d:

    # Zt "Damn it... I was ready to find out more about her."
    Zt "Maldita sea... estaba listo para averiguar más sobre ella."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:44
translate spanish d2a_home_3e9d3de3:

    # Zt "Anyway... chasing her would be a waste of time. I should head back to the palace and report to the Queen."
    Zt "De todos modos... perseguirla sería una pérdida de tiempo. Debería volver al palacio e informar a la Reina."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:46
translate spanish d2a_home_1540c09f:

    # Zt "That little statue should get me a nice reward from the Queen."
    Zt "Esa pequeña estatua debería conseguirme una buena recompensa de la Reina."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:48
translate spanish d2a_home_7927d264:

    # Zt "Coming before the Queen without the statue in my hand won't be pretty."
    Zt "Presentarme ante la Reina sin la estatua en la mano no será agradable."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:50
translate spanish d2a_home_15981647:

    # Zt "I should head to the palace. That little statue should get me a nice reward from the Queen."
    Zt "Debería dirigirme al palacio. Esa pequeña estatua debería darme una buena recompensa de la Reina."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:58
