translate spanish d2b_3bf5f855:

    # Z "Let [Ta] be an example to you. She's polite, doesn't talk too much and lets me pass through."
    Z "Que [Ta] te sirva de ejemplo. Es educada, no habla demasiado y me deja pasar."

