    S "..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1067
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_87b94eb2:

    # Z "No...!"
    Z "¡No...!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1071
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_07a78323:

    # Z "This can't be... real..."
    Z "Esto no puede ser... real..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1075
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_a6f7fff2:

    # Z "It can't be..."
    Z "No puede ser..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1079
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_b655a073:

    # Z "Akh-"
    Z "Akh-"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1086
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_2a276d16:

    # "The mummy lunged at you, causing you to fall and never get up again."
    "La momia se lanzó contra ti, provocando que cayeras y no volvieras a levantarte."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1087
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_9f360b17:

    # "[S]'s corpse got devoured. Her bones will be a reminder for future travellers, if any should ever dare to enter these tombs again."
    "El cadáver de [S] fue devorado. Sus huesos serán un recordatorio para futuros viajeros, si es que alguno se atreve a entrar de nuevo en estas tumbas."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1101
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_1aea7013:

    # Z "[S], get down!"
    Z "[S], ¡agáchate!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1104
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_7098ca64:

    # Z "NOW!!"
    Z "¡¡AHORA!!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1109
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_a3c68a48:

    # S "...!"
    S "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1112
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_224030d3:

    # Z "Fuck... you!"
    Z "¡Que te... jodan!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1113
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_90aa9ae5:

    # S "Stay still, [persistent.dad]!!"
    S "¡Quédate quieto, ¡¡[persistent.dad]!!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1119
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_8ddb42cd:

    # Mum "...!"
    Mum "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1123
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_b84a803a:

    # Z "Whew..."
    Z "Uf..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1124
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_b4664552:

    # S "Whoa... my... first fight against mummies!"
    S "¡Guau... mi... primera pelea contra momias!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1125
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_a05f6563:

    # Z "That was intense."
    Z "Eso fue intenso."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1126
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_f716e211:

    # S "Let's see if it was worth it."
    S "Veamos si ha merecido la pena."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1129
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_67c96e8a:

    # S "Oh this is a good haul."
    S "¡Oh, esto es un buen botín!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1130
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_a45ae5fa:

    # Z "I can see why they held on to it for so long."
    Z "Ya veo por qué se han aferrado a ella durante tanto tiempo."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1133
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_3e7a21ed:

    # S "I wonder about the ones we fought... what it meant to them..."
    S "Me pregunto por los que lucharon contra nosotros... qué significaba para ellos..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1136
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_5a3d40ad:

    # Z "We better leave this knowledge buried. However, if there were mummies around, then there's probably something rotting not far away."
    Z "Será mejor que dejemos enterrado este conocimiento. Sin embargo, si había momias por aquí, probablemente haya algo pudriéndose no muy lejos."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1137
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_2892642d:

    # Z "Let's get ready to leave. It should be dark outside by now. And I don't want to breathe in this stale stench for any longer than I have to."
    Z "Preparémonos para salir. Ya debe estar oscuro afuera. Y no quiero respirar este hedor rancio más tiempo del necesario."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1140
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_28ea3060:

    # S "Yes... just give me a minute. I just conquered my first ever treasure. {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "Sí... dame un minuto. Acabo de conquistar mi primer tesoro. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1141
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_031b7308:

    # Z "Take your time, but do not dally too long. We still need to bring this back to the car."
    Z "Tómate tu tiempo, pero no te demores demasiado. Aún necesitamos llevar esto de vuelta al coche."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1144
translate spanish d2e_shani_attacked_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1157
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_0fde68c3:

    # S "Can you carry the rest...? I want to try something."
    S "¿Puedes cargar el resto...? Quiero probar algo."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1158
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5447afbc:

    # Z "Okay... but what is that?"
    Z "Vale... ¿pero qué es eso?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1159
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_173fb277:

    # S "You will see!"
    S "¡Ya lo verás!"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1162
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_1c9c507d:

    # Zt "Okay... that should be it. Everything is packed and ready..."
    Zt "Bien... eso debería ser todo. Todo está empaquetado y listo..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1163
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5246a43e:

    # Zt "Now... where is my girl..."
    Zt "Ahora... ¿dónde está mi chica...?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1166
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_65781c81:

    # "You turn around..."
    "Te das la vuelta..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1167
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_b0f93c15:

    # Zt "What is she..."
    Zt "¿Qué es lo que...?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1168
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_f3cb9106:

    # Z "[S]! What are you doing up there?"
    Z "¡[S]! ¿Qué haces ahí arriba?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1171
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_0c8c28d6:

    # Zt "Climbing up there... this is dangerous, how did she even get up there?"
    Zt "Subir ahí arriba... esto es peligroso, ¿cómo ha llegado hasta ahí?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1174
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_a3a8df19:

    # "You climb up the bricks, one by one, until you reach the top of the entrance..."
    "Subes los ladrillos, uno por uno, hasta llegar a la cima de la entrada..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1177
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5f0eb335:

    # Z "[S]... {i}*pant*{/i}"
    Z "[S]... {i}*jadeos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1178
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_63a89250:

    # Z "Why are we here?"
    Z "¿Por qué estamos aquí?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1180
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_dcacbfca:

    # S "No reason, really..."
    S "Sin razón, realmente..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1183
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_01eb80a8:

    # S "Just enjoying the view..."
    S "Solo disfrutando de la vista..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1184
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1187
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_964995a8:

    # "You sit down, next to her..."
    "Te sientas a su lado..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1190
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_0d186ca0:

    # Z "This is a nice view indeed..."
    Z "Esto es una vista agradable de verdad..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1194
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_43b9c472:

    # Z "You did well today."
    Z "Hoy lo has hecho bien."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1197
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_13fceeda:

    # S "I was so nervous."
    S "Estaba muy nerviosa."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1198
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_e1dded8c:

    # S "First the impaled skull, then the sleeping mummies."
    S "Primero el cráneo empalado, luego las momias dormidas."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1202
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_83f1868c:

    # S "But I thought about earlier, when you said you got my back if anything happens."
    S "Pero pensé en lo de antes, cuando dijiste que me cubrías las espaldas si pasaba algo."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1203
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_beb2627d:

    # S "That helped a lot."
    S "Eso ayudó mucho."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1205
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_9a233961:

    # S "But I thought about earlier, when you said I need to trust in myself."
    S "Pero pensé en lo de antes, cuando dijiste que tenía que confiar en mí misma."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1206
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_beb2627d_1:

    # S "That helped a lot."
    S "Eso ayudó mucho."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1209
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_4203439e:

    # Z "I'm glad."
    Z "Me alegro."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1212
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5bdb5b4a:

    # S "Say..."
    S "Dime..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1213
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_8aee7782:

    # S "How do you... {i}*sigh*"
    S "¿Cómo... {i}Suspiro*{/i}?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1216
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_64b84ebd:

    # Z "How do I what?"
    Z "¿Cómo hago qué?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1219
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_532b0423:

    # S "How do you even... cope with all this?"
    S "¿Cómo te enfrentas... a todo esto?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1220
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_714d7512:

    # S "I mean what did we ever do to deserve to live with cursed storms or buried mummies..."
    S "Quiero decir, ¿qué hicimos para merecer vivir con tormentas malditas o momias enterradas...?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1221
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_975616e0:

    # S "Or dead megacities that only tell us stories about a world long gone?"
    S "¿O megalópolis muertas que solo nos cuentan historias de un mundo perdido hace mucho tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1224
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_6336a3c3:

    # S "Why are we not allowed to experience such a life as they must once have had?"
    S "¿Por qué no se nos permite experimentar una vida como la que debieron tener?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1227
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_544bb88d:

    # S "How come we can't seem to find a way to rebuild?!"
    S "¿Cómo es posible que no encontremos la manera de reconstruirlo?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1230
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1231
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5592cbbd:

    # Z "I don't have an answer to your questions..."
    Z "No tengo respuesta a tus preguntas..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1232
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5b244e99:

    # Z "But sometimes, I believe that we were put here to be tested."
    Z "Pero a veces, creo que nos pusieron aquí para ponernos a prueba."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1233
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_d5294197:

    # Z "Maybe not by someone or something, and maybe for no reason at all."
    Z "Tal vez no por alguien o algo, y tal vez por ninguna razón en absoluto."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1236
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_01a7c440:

    # Z "Maybe it's just bad luck, that we are born in this moment in time, and things could and will indeed be a lot better than they are right now."
    Z "Tal vez sólo sea mala suerte, que hayamos nacido en este momento, y las cosas podrían ser y serán de hecho mucho mejores de lo que son ahora."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1237
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_60da162d:

    # Z "The point I'm getting at is this:"
    Z "A lo que quiero llegar es a esto:"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1238
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_9ce8f33c:

    # Z "The question, in the end, is always what you do with the life you are given."
    Z "La cuestión, al final, es siempre lo que haces con la vida que te dan."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1239
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_df998bda:

    # Z "No matter how hard it may seem."
    Z "No importa lo duro que pueda parecer."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1240
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_3f3d3e07:

    # Z "There is no alternative to this one life you have."
    Z "No hay alternativa a esta única vida que tienes."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1241
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_9504b13a:

    # Z "Non-existence is something you can't experience."
    Z "La inexistencia es algo que no puedes experimentar."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1242
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_8128f152:

    # Z "And if we can't change the time we were born in..."
    Z "Y si no podemos cambiar el tiempo en el que nacimos..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1243
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5df081aa:

    # Z "We might as well make the best of it while we can."
    Z "Podríamos también sacarle el máximo provecho mientras podamos."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1246
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1249
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_af389521:

    # S "But what do you mean by \"make the best out of it\"?"
    S "Pero ¿qué quieres decir con \"aprovecharlo al máximo\"?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1250
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_e6f49596:

    # S "What to do with those who abuse their power to ruin other lives..."
    S "¿Qué hacer con los que abusan de su poder para arruinar otras vidas..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1251
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_a88766b4:

    # S "...only because it profits theirs?"
    S "... ¿sólo porque les beneficia a ellos?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1254
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_7ec353b9:

    # S "What about those who work so hard day in day out to help others?"
    S "¿Qué pasa con los que trabajan tan duro día a día para ayudar a los demás?"

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1263
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_f3dd1dc2:

    # Z "Everyone has a reason for why they are who they are."
    Z "Todos tienen una razón para ser quienes son."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1264
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_5ccad5ed:

    # Z "But we all should try to make the world a better place while we're here."
    Z "Pero todos debemos intentar hacer del mundo un lugar mejor mientras estemos aquí."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1265
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_d9a98784:

    # Z "Just like those who came before us did."
    Z "Tal y como hicieron los que nos precedieron."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1266
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_db33cda4:

    # S "But the world is in ruins."
    S "Pero el mundo está en ruinas."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1267
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_89b4b9ce:

    # Z "That doesn't mean that anyone back then wanted things to be this way."
    Z "Eso no significa que alguien quisiera que las cosas fueran así en ese entonces."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1268
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_1c01fbca:

    # Z "Just like there are more than enough people alive today who work for Zeta to be a better place for everyone."
    Z "Al igual que hay más que suficientes personas vivas hoy en día que trabajan para que Zeta sea un lugar mejor para todos."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1269
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_2651cc9b:

    # Z "But in the end the people in charge bear the greatest responsibility..."
    Z "Pero al final los responsables tienen la mayor responsabilidad..."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1277
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_be30969c:

    # Z "There are those who work for a better society and then there are those who don't."
    Z "Hay quienes trabajan por una sociedad mejor y luego están los que no lo hacen."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1278
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_b05bc056:

    # Z "But that is because every person has different motivations."
    Z "Pero eso es porque cada persona tiene diferentes motivaciones."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1279
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_2765eb7d:

    # Z "You will get to know some of the decayed tomorrow."
    Z "Mañana conocerás a algunos de los decaídos."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1280
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_1f515056:

    # Z "Most of them don't have anything to live for anymore."
    Z "La mayoría ya no tiene nada por lo que vivir."

# game/scripts/day2.rpy:1281
translate spanish d2e_leaving_tomb_7dee628e:

